<span id="freeTextContainer2275609137816122192">After a fantastic Road Scholar trip to the Italian Lake District, I was eager to try to replicate some of the regional specialties we ate on our journey. Lynn Kasper has done a brilliant job of adapting these recipes for American cooks. I especially appreciate the way many recipes include make-ahead tips--I&apos;m much more likely to try those!</span>
